            "content": "<p>Finding the perfect <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/all-rings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"RIng\">ring</a> can be overwhelming for all the meaning it holds - love, celebration and timeless beauty and even on finding the ring, one crucial detail decides it all - the right ring size. The perfect ring size ensures comfort, assurance that it won’t fall off, and most importantly, decides the way it sits, shines and complements your hand. That’s why knowing your ring size is the first step to deciding a truly personal piece, as if it was crafted just for you! </p>",
